Package: ImageArtR
Title: Turn Images into Artistic Graphics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zhou", "Shirong", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zsrnog@yeah.net")
  )
Description: Provides a consistent set of tools for reading, preprocessing,
    transforming, plotting, and saving images as circle packing art, mosaics,
    outlines, sketches, cartoons, and color palettes. Functions return a common
    S3 object so results can be printed, plotted, summarized, and saved with a
    unified interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
